    {
      "id": "context-grammar-smoke-instructions",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Expected Results",
      "position": {
        "x": 720,
        "y": 20
      },
      "width": 520,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Expected Results\n\n## Expand\n- Click `Expand Script Scope Graph`.\n- The target graph should materialize in place as an expanded projection.\n- The host graph should remain the host session.\n- Imported execution nodes should remain downgraded/blocked unless authority later moves there.\n\n## Bridge\n- Click `Bridge Smoke Class`.\n- A bright yellow markdown node should appear next to the bridge port with visible content.\n- The created node should stay in this fragment.\n- Its data should include `_bridge.sourceRef` and local fragment provenance.\n\n## Quick check\n- `expand` stretches the world.\n- `bridge` imports a capability locally.\n- neither operation should replace the host graph.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false
      }
    }
